    {
      "id": "PopularPost37301",
      "post_content": "That ability is pretty darned expensive, though really awesome at the same time. Can attack then untap everything to get around blockers in the second combat phase. It seems like it needs to end a game though, rather than be played every turn, since the mana drawback would catch up to you eventually. Could defintley see a game win with broodmate dragons and this hellkite charger though, attack with all, kill all blockers, then attack again for 21.  \n  \nNature's will would just be insane with this card if you could ever get both into play. Garruk wildspeaker also, because he would both help with the mana cost, but if you ever got his ultimate going and your charger at the same time you get a double over run in one turn.",
      "posted_by": "Donovan_Fabian",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost37301\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">That ability is pretty darned expensive, though really awesome at the same time.  Can attack then untap everything to get around blockers in the second combat phase.  It seems like it needs to end a game though, rather than be played every turn, since the mana drawback would catch up to you eventually.  Could defintley see a game win with broodmate dragons and this hellkite charger though, attack with all, kill all blockers, then attack again for 21.<br/><br/>Nature's will would just be insane with this card if you could ever get both into play.  Garruk wildspeaker also, because he would both help with the mana cost, but if you ever got his ultimate going and your charger at the same time you get a double over run in one turn.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '37301'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2942\">Donovan_Fabian</span>\r\n                                (12/10/2009 7:32:12 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" i