    {
      "id": "PopularPost44813",
      "post_content": "I think in a limited format, this guy is pretty incredible. Most of the comments make it sound like you MUST pay for his ability and him on the same turn... hardly. As a 5/5, he is tough enough to manage for a turn, and since he is hasted your're going to get one shot in at the bare minimum.\n  \n   \nNot a massive game winner, but a very tougb flyer with a potentially game-ending ability on the turn after he hits the table.\n  \n   \n4/5\n  ",
