    {
      "id": "PopularPost62408",
      "post_content": "With the new Bear Umbra coming out for Eldrazi... If you have 10 mana handy, you can cast the hasty dragon, put Bear Umbra on it and get infinite attacking phases. The only way the opponent can stop you is if they bounce the Dragon or destroy it in response to the Umbra being cast. If they destroy it as it attacks, you still get to attack again since the Umbra protects it once.  \n  \nLooks like a fun combo to play :P",
